{"id":"obal","term":"Obal","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Stripped, the eight son of Joktan (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 10:28\">Gen. 10:28</a>); called also Ebal (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:22\">1 Chr. 1:22</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 10:28","1 Chronicles 1:22"]}